 and the Gold (TV)\">The Red Dragon and the Gold</a>\"</li>\n<li>\"<a href=\"/index.php/Regent_(TV)\" title=\"Regent (TV)\">Regent</a>\"</li>\n<li>\"<a href=\"/index.php/Smallfolk_(TV)\" title=\"Smallfolk (TV)\">Smallfolk</a>\"</li>\n<li>\"<a href=\"/index.php/The_Red_Sowing_(TV)\" title=\"The Red Sowing (TV)\">The Red Sowing</a>\"</li>\n<li>\"<a href=\"/index.php/The_Queen_Who_Ever_Was\" title=\"The Queen Who Ever Was\">The Queen Who Ever Was</a>\"</li></ul>\n</div></td></tr><tr style=\"height:2px\"><td></td></tr><tr><td scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\";;\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_of_the_Dragon_-_Season_3\" title=\"House of the Dragon - Season 3\">Season 3</a></td><td style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px;;;\" class=\"navbox-list navbox-odd\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li>TBD</li></ul>\n</div></td></tr><tr style=\"height:2px\"><td></td></tr><tr><td scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\";;\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_of_the_Dragon_-_Season_4\" title=\"House of the Dragon - Season 4\">Season 4</a></td><td style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px;;;\" class=\"navbox-list navbox-even\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li>TBD</li></ul>\n</div></td></tr><tr style=\"height:2px\"><td></td></tr><tr><td scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\";;\">Other</td><td style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px;;;\" class=\"navbox-list navbox-odd\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Differences_between_Fire_%26_Blood_and_House_of_the_Dragon\" title=\"Differences between Fire &amp; Blood and House of the Dragon\">Differences in adaptation</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/List_of_actors_of_House_of_the_Dragon\" title=\"List of actors of House of the Dragon\">List of actors</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/List_of_characters_created_for_House_of_th